It should also be noted that other MSS. pre- served in Germany have been by some reckoned to be of primary importance, namely one (now lost) called ‘Hummelianus' (H), and two others at Munich and Stuttgart (M and S), all of which are maintained to be derived from copies taken of the old MS. before it came into the possession of Asculanus ⁴.
